@id: 7c3e
a page ruled by the diagram of the sentences: the diagram and the chosen sentence sit on the left as the only navigation, the code sits on the right, and nothing speaks until a node is clicked. no toggles, no instructions; the only chrome is the project bar top left and the file name above the code. the page reads the compiler's json and decides nothing.

note: v3 of the renderer. the panes-and-hover chrome is gone; the poset is the interface.
